description: Defines an enum EventStatus and a class MaintenanceEvent representing maintenance events with properties like id, title, status, cost, color, date, and vehicleId; includes a copyWith method for immutability.

classes.name: MaintenanceEvent
classes.description: Represents a maintenance event with properties such as id, title, status, cost, color, date, and vehicleId.

methods.name: copyWith
methods.description: Creates a copy of MaintenanceEvent with optional new values for its fields, allowing immutability.
